    "For instance, hesitant or stuttering speech might point to a lack of understanding, while an enthusiastic tone could imply interest.",
    "The students' engagement analyzed this way can help adjust teaching strategies accordingly.The limitations of this system may include the variability in students' expressive behaviors and the subtlety of some emotional cues.",
